					</p>

			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
    
    
    
<div class="row">

<div class="col-md-12">

    <p>This is where I will do profile management.</p>
    
    <ul>
    <li>User email, change password</li>
    <li>Link to Google+ login</li>
    <li>Role management</li>
    </ul>
    
    <hr>
    
    <em>Roles:</em>
    
    <ul>
    <li>Viewer: only look at main screen and logs, no access to the rest. No connection rights.</li>
    <li>Operator: create/delete devices, read/write access</li>
    <li>Administrator: same as operator + create users</li>
    </ul>
    </div>
